Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 12/31/2024

TrackYourGoals - Savings ("the App") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your data. This Privacy Policy outlines how the App handles user data.

1. No Data Collection
The App does not collect, store, or process any personal information or data. All information you input into the App (e.g., financial goals, savings targets) is stored locally on your device and is not shared with external servers or third parties.

2. Local Data Storage
Any data entered into the App, such as goals and progress, is saved locally on your device.
No information is transmitted to external servers, ensuring your privacy and security.
3. Third-Party Services
The App does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking tools. Your activity within the App remains completely private.

4. User Rights
As the App does not collect data, there is no personal information to access, modify, or delete. You can delete any data you’ve entered directly from the App by uninstalling it.

5. Changes to This Policy
If changes are made to the App’s functionality that may affect privacy, this Privacy Policy will be updated accordingly. Any changes will be communicated clearly within the App.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at: Email: felipemendesdiz@gmail.com

